00:20:05.446 --> 00:20:07.366
that they are correctly
tapping on that button.

00:20:08.046 --> 00:20:09.706
We call this the
highlighted state.

00:20:09.706 --> 00:20:11.796
So what I'm going to do
now is I'm also going

00:20:11.796 --> 00:20:12.956
to change my highlighted state.

