upload your ad to your device

00:41:49.116 --> 00:41:51.156
and you can try it out
right inside of iOS.

00:41:52.036 --> 00:41:54.616
This is also really great
for testing the performance

00:41:54.616 --> 00:41:56.786
of your ad as it downloads
over the cellular network

00:41:56.786 --> 00:41:57.986
which is an important
consideration.

00:41:58.536 --> 00:42:02.126
